data.description: Welcome to Steubing Ranch! Beautiful kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances, additional cabinets/countertop installed, and granite countertops throughout. 2 main bedrooms (1 upstairs & 1 downstairs). Downstairs primary bathroom has double vanity sinks and walk-in closet. Upstairs you are met with a spacious game room that can easily be converted to a 5th bedroom. Other additional rooms are located upstairs and each have ceiling fans within them. Laundry room is upstairs and home comes with a water softener. Huge backyard with a deck surrounding your above ground pool. Close proximity to Steubing Ranch and Longs Creek elementary and Harris Middle School, very close access to loop 1604, and just a short trip to Randolph AFB. Within minutes of Bulverede Shopping Center and Bulverde Marketplace where your neighborhood HEB is located.
